Look Up now shows personalized suggestions from the web, iTunes, the App Store, movie showtimes, nearby locations, and more.
You can adjust this in Settings.
Messages can show you suggestions for images, animated gifs, and videos to share based on what’s popular, the content of your messages, and your location.

Safari search now shows personalized suggestions from the web, iTunes, the App Store, movie showtimes, nearby locations, and more.
You can adjust this in Settings.
You can search the web, your contacts, nearby locations, and see personalized suggestions as you type. You can adjust this in Settings.
Look Up finds results about the content of your photo from the web, the App Store, nearby locations, and more. You can adjust this in Settings.
Look Up shows personalized suggestions based on the content of your photo from the web, iTunes, the App Store, movie showtimes, nearby locations, and more. You can adjust this in Settings.
